      • updateParentNet

        public org.apache.commons.math3.complex.Complex updateParentNet()
        Description copied from interface: IBusChildNetHelper
        Update the bus state using the child Network object. Return the power mismatch between the swing bus of the child Network and the corresponding parent net bus. The mismatch is used to determine the convergence of the multi-net loadflow calculation.
        Specified by:
        updateParentNet in interface IBusChildNetHelper<AclfBus,AclfBus>
        Returns:
        power mismatch between the swing bus of the child Network and the corresponding parent net bus

      • updateParentNet

        Description copied from interface: IBusChildNetHelper
        Update the bus state using the swingPQ, It is called by the updateBus() method. In case of Grid computing, swingPQ might be from a remote node. Return the power mismatch of the bus.
        Specified by:
